Let's add input for test and expected output to automate the testing of
Luna.

Lack of error handling for incorrect inputs from user

and update function to catch potential errors

Using new exception class allows us to isolate the error to bad inputs
from user

No functionality to delete added tasks

1. modify the main function to allow users to delete tasks from their
   list of tasks
2. Change how tasks is stored from array to ArrayList

Using ArrayList allows easy deletion and addition of Tasks over array.
